We urge our members not to give in to provocations, whatever the anarchists want to do, it's their responsibility, not ours.

@radical
subtitle: Let the demonstration proceed naturally.
on-arrival: revolutionary_strength += 5; radicalization -= 1; reformist_dissent += 5; fai_ties += 1
